"force-displacement curve at the loaded edge, traced through the load / "
"unload cycle."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/plasticity_strip.rst:143
#: 2a38c4fde2f447439aaca86c01990571
msgid ""
"The force-displacement curve is the canonical signature of plasticity: "
"linear elastic loading until yield, a hardening branch above "
":math:`\\sigma_y`, then a linear elastic unloading branch back to a non-"
"zero residual displacement at zero load."
msgstr ""

